params.name: data.parent
params.description: Required. The name of the location that contains the entry groups, which can be provided in URL format. Example: * projects/{project_id}/locations/{location}

params.name: data.page_size
params.description: Optional. The maximum number of items to return. Default is 10. Max limit is 1000. Throws an invalid argument for page_size > 1000.

params.name: data.page_token
params.description: Optional. Token that specifies which page is requested. If empty, the first page is returned.
